CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 7, 1964, pg. 7, reads: "Mr. and Mrs. Charles Golphin...recently married"
TitMainTitle: Groom Charles Golphin wearing bow tie and jacket with satin lapels, and bride wearing gown with lace overlay and mid length veil, standing behind three tiered wedding cake in interior with twisted crepe paper streamers
